# random duel scenario with two territories for each team

# Of course, this config file goes best with either
#MaxTeams 4
#AllianceSize 2
# or
#MaxTeams 2
#TerritoriesPerTeam 2

# There are too many possibilities here to list them all,
# so let's just go by guidelines. Pick Territory1 as a southern
# territory and avoid making its direct northern neighbour an enemy.
# Do so my making it randomly an ally or empty.

RBegin
Territory1 SouthAmerica
RSet Territory2 NorthAmerica
RSet Territory6 NorthAmerica
Randomise
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 Africa
RSet Territory2 Europe
RSet Territory6 Europe
Randomise
REnd

RBegin
Territory1 Asia
RSet Territory2 Russia
RSet Territory6 Russia
Randomise
REnd

Randomise
